overview: Ram Mohan Rao and Shyamala Bharath both are political rivals. Ram Mohan Rao is the chief minister of the Andhra Pradesh state. And shyamala Bharath is the opposition party leader. She is a brave and powerful leader. She can command the police department, leaders, and goons. From the last two state assembly elections, she has been making an effort to becomne the chief minister.
title: Sasanasabha
